Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起旅行果然很让人兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩到尽兴呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然要是没有作业的话  这也许就是趟没有后顾之忧的旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才到7月  玩的时候就忘掉作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是暑假的生存之道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从痛苦的事情里转移视线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:41.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}高兴地活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之后会好好做的  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一声  我作业已经搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我抄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本就不是好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微花了点时间准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是和伊御同学第一次去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的那样的准备都很辛苦的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学  小姬  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有比较希望坐在窗边的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬容易晕车吧  坐在窗边比较好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是那么不擅长乘坐交通工具  没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果被突然袭击鼻子流血…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会流呢  再说突然袭击是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然袭击就是…我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  小姬就请坐窗边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击坠两人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不能大意露出破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御庭果然是坐伊御身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该坐在膝盖上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个大晴天真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子好像会讨厌电车的声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咯当咕咚=咯当五吨=五吨五吨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是显得很重吗  这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1060,110)}洋葱×2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:20.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1060,110)}命中判定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.99,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子才没有五吨啦	
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.16,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼  我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱是从哪儿拿出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说榊没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,200)}好孩子不要模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样接下来就不要换乘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  悠闲地慢慢坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指目标  轨迹都被决定好的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目的地之前都被决定好了的铁轨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有驾照  倒是想试试开车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同学要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去把决定好的铁轨扳开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来是白纸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要自己好好想想再行动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去买饮料…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买零食来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要出发了  姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了商店  但是还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机没带出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是去卫生间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬在大家的心里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在心里  但也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买来稀有的零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬回来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木  姬回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门要关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下再碰头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御  你在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易和大家一起来旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把你一个人丢在这种地方  会寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是月水木到最后都在找姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按你说的算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(980,150)}等下一班电车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬她们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有榊在  应该没事的  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非伊御留下来  是为了不让女孩子一个人什…什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一遍感觉有点害臊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊同学  为什么没有阻止他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让女孩子落单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很危险的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然能够理解榊同学和伊御同学的这种温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么如果伊御被落下的时候该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗户把御庭丢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能叫做贴心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(980,200)}总算集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御君  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吓了一跳呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再做那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边看着的人都觉得担心  想做点什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是虽说如此  我内心其实也是战战兢兢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊同学其实很兴奋的呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起了好多鸡皮疙瘩都快变成鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本最大的淡水湖  野鸟声息地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时就把你送去琵琶湖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野鸟大竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有伊御同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}错过了拥抱的时机……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬  看招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天  在水边嬉戏的少女的欢声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}德国莱茵河的回音石  有女妖用歌声引诱渔船触礁的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就仿佛像罗勒莱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那种歌声钓上钩的话会溺水的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去溺一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,400)}垂钓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然的桥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲跳会很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真宵同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵扑通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊同学  给我钓饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  钓饵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵扑通  再临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你钓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请正常地把我拖上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然会被月水木同学钓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一条鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,250)}稍事休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  总觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会倒向这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果倒向这边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是肩膀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖  膝盖？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝枕啊…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒向这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}无法抗拒的未知力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的倒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要是想…要是想睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给你也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝…膝盖什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起过来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御君在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…再让我休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这发展好像错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的头放上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这睡姿真萌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸  摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝枕  我拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春  我拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,10)}会吵醒他的  所以身体不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会醒过来的哦  会醒过来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃肉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉  烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了  还没准备好吗  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还有一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御君你要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们换着烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会吃的  你们别在意吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御  喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉串差不多要烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御  喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锡箔纸里的肉也要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御  喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学  你在吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}无限循环
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉肉  肉肉  接着还是肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是还是肉肉  要吃好多肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉肉  肉肉  接着还是肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.33,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一个劲只吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是还是肉肉  要吃好多肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.41,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜和鱼也要好好吃才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:04.10,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不吃各种食物营养是会失衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说写上像「肉肉蔬菜肉鱼」这样的旋律对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  旋律吗  那么我的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「牛牛牛猪牛猪牛牛鸡」 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是肉的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吃蔬菜去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御同学也要刻上旋律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋律什么的我不太在意  在适当时机我会掺杂吃蔬菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该就是「肉肉蔬菜」这样的旋律的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那样的话大概就是吃不腻的那种好吃的吃法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  那么月水木同学的旋律就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「LOVE LOVE 伊御同学 喜欢喜欢 亲亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢  亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饱好饱哦  已经什么都吃不进了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点撑  感觉有点吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉吃的东西都要撑破肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我是爸爸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才什么东西飞过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍开个玩笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到去旅行什么的通常都会有偷窥女澡堂的活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这话还真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥并不是目的  在这个过程里紧张的心情才是最大的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是一种奇景吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说的话  我也能懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是结果来说要是看到了要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计就会很兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种微妙不爽感就无法平复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖等她们出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,450)}洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣形态  GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很适合你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这幅符合夏天的身姿如何喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真宵是浴衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有旅馆的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是件不错的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一样嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到浴衣  月水木同学  给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊这个啊  会转圈圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会「哎呀」一声  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没有转圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是还有必要跟着来「哎呀」一声？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学要把头发弄干还真是累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木  我帮你弄干头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我自己弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托小姬弄吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}\N\N一\N不\N小\N心\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意　过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的不是…那是口误…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  准备得也差不多了  我们开始干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大的组合  我也买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他零零碎碎的也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然一说到暑假的夜晚就是烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要放哪个呢  好纠结的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落伞  要发射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  GO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样很疼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(980,660)}火箭烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀了我吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火以后我也不知道为啥会往你那边飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一发要好好的丢到别的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着天空！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大火箭设置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有5秒钟发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然又！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}线香花火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42}我们来玩「线香花火可以保持越久的人说明和大家的感情越好」的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连说明都不用的标题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开工了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  GO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…想出这种悲剧游戏的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来决一次胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学要是先结束了就是两厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月水木同学要是先结束了就是两厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花都是消纵即逝的  但是因为太美总会长留在人们的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  盛开即谢的花朵之美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊御  给这些在看烟花的姑娘们的心跳导火线上放一把火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意中让我看到的你的笑容　比烟花更加美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会永留我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是夏日里绽开的两朵红花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是风雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好  还行  还成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里那里幼稚园
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来搞好关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现月水木了
